data.description:
Recently painted open concept condo in great walkable neighborhood. Light and bright space with full wall of windows offering a City View. Stainless steel appliances. Great storage pantry. Walk in closet with built in storage.

Lease is 12 months. Tenant pays electric. No smoking. No pets. Water and G fiber cable included in rent. One parking space with unit.
